Package org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.service.connection

Interface ConnectionDetails

All Known Subinterfaces:
ActiveMQConnectionDetails, CassandraConnectionDetails, CouchbaseConnectionDetails, ElasticsearchConnectionDetails, FlywayConnectionDetails, JdbcConnectionDetails, KafkaConnectionDetails, LiquibaseConnectionDetails, MongoConnectionDetails, Neo4jConnectionDetails, OtlpMetricsConnectionDetails, OtlpTracingConnectionDetails, PulsarConnectionDetails, R2dbcConnectionDetails, RabbitConnectionDetails, RedisConnectionDetails, ZipkinConnectionDetails
All Known Implementing Classes:
ContainerConnectionDetailsFactory.ContainerConnectionDetails, DockerComposeConnectionDetailsFactory.DockerComposeConnectionDetails, PropertiesMongoConnectionDetails
public interface ConnectionDetails
Base interface for types that provide the details required to establish a connection to a remote service.

Implementation classes can also implement OriginProvider in order to provide origin information.

3.1.0
